article.description: James Dickey had 12 points and eight rebounds as UNC Greensboro rolled past Tennessee Tech 64-30 on Friday night.
article.headline: Dickey leads UNC-Greensboro past Tennessee Tech 64-30
article.linkText: Dickey leads UNC-Greensboro past Tennessee Tech 64-30
article.story: GREENSBORO, N.C. -- James Dickey had 12 points and eight rebounds as UNC Greensboro rolled past Tennessee Tech 64-30 on Friday night. Michael Hueitt Jr. had 11 points for UNC Greensboro (3-1). Isaiah Miller added 11 points and Kyrin Galloway had three blocks. Darius Allen scored seven points and Jr. Clay had eight rebounds and four points for the Golden Eagles (1-3). UNC Greensboro takes on Montana State at home on Saturday. Tennessee Tech faces Appalachian State on Saturday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
